      'LocalDateTable_d1613991-c06c-46b5-94c4-537852371fcf'[Ano],

      __DS0FilterTable,
      __DS0FilterTable2,
      "SumTotal_Desempregados", CALCULATE(SUM('Desemprego'[Total_Desempregados]))
    )

  VAR __ScopedCoreDM0 = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(
        SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
          'LocalDateTable_d1613991-c06c-46b5-94c4-537852371fcf'[Ano],
          'LocalDateTable_d1613991-c06c-46b5-94c4-537852371fcf'[Trimestre],

          __DS0FilterTable,
          __DS0FilterTable2,
          "MinDate", IGNORE(CALCULATE(MIN('LocalDateTable_d1613991-c06c-46b5-94c4-537852371fcf'[Date])))
        )
      ),
      OR(

          OR(
            OR(
              OR(
                NOT(ISBLANK('LocalDateTable_d1613991-c06c-46b5-94c4-537852371fcf'[Ano])),
                NOT(ISBLANK('LocalDateTable_d1613991-c06c-46b5-94c4-537852371fcf'[Trimestre]))

            ),

        ),
        NOT(ISBLANK('LocalDateTable_d1613991-c06c-46b5-94c4-537852371fcf'[Dia]))
      )
    )

  VAR __DS0Core = 
    NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
      __ScopedCoreI0,
      __ScopedCoreDM0
    )

      COUNTROWS(

          'LocalDateTable_d1613991-c06c-46b5-94c4-537852371fcf'[Trimestre],

        )
      )
    )

  VAR __DS0SecondaryDbCount = 
    CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'Desemprego'[Range_Idade])))

  VAR __DS0BodyBinnedSample = 
    SAMPLEAXISWITHLOCALMINMAX(
      3500,
      __DS0Core,
      [MinDate],
      [SumTotal_Desempregados],
      350,
      'Desemprego'[Range_Idade],
      ALPHABETICAL,
      ASC,
      105000,
      60
    )

  VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
    SUMMARIZE(__DS0BodyBinnedSample, 'Desemprego'[Range_Idade])

  VAR __DS0SecondaryCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0SecondaryBase))

  VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
    SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(

      "ColumnIndex",
      __DS0SecondaryBase,
      'Desemprego'[Range_Idade],
      ASC
    )

    "DS0PrimaryDbCount", __DS0PrimaryDbCount,
    "DS0SecondaryDbCount", __DS0SecondaryDbCount,
    "DS0SecondaryCount", __DS0SecondaryCount
  )

EVALUATE
  __DS0SecondaryBase
